| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5949 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f28dc9df-400d-5e6b-9c46-addeda03b9c8"
